# Summary
The User Sessions chart in Amplitude enables analysis of session-based metrics including session length distribution, average session length, and sessions per user, helping teams understand engagement frequency and duration across different user segments. The chart uses a Sessions Module rather than Events Module and offers various measurement options including Total Sessions, Time Spent, Length Distribution, and custom formulas.

